    <div class="well" id="amazon-kindle-real-life-review" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://gizmodo.com/gadgets/our-kindle-verdict/amazon-kindle-real+life-review-verdict-lightweight-long-lasting-and-easy-to-grip-in-bed-325939.php">Amazon Kindle Real-Life Review (Verdict: Lightweight, Long Lasting and Easy to Grip... In Bed)</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Best review I&#8217;ve seen of the Kindle so far.  I&#8217;d be tempted to get one, but for the much-noted DRM restrictions.  If I&#8217;m unable to &#8220;lend&#8221; or &#8220;borrow&#8221; e-books I&#8217;ve purchased, like I currently can with dead-tree, then it&#8217;s of no interest to me.</p>

